snippet.title: Magic Mike XXL (2015) Behind the Scenes Movie Interview - Amber Heard is 'Zoe'
snippet.description:

Magic Mike XXL Behind the Scenes Movie Interview - Amber Heard is 'Zoe' directed by Gregory Jacobs and starring Elizabeth Banks, Amber Heard, Channing Tatum.
Courtesy of: Warner Bros. Pictures

Plot:
Three years after Mike bowed out of the stripper life at the top of his game, he and the remaining Kings of Tampa hit the road to Myrtle Beach to put on one last blow-out performance.

Genre: Comedy, Drama, Music
Director: Gregory Jacobs
Cast: Elizabeth Banks, Amber Heard, Channing Tatum, Matt Bomer, Joe Manganiello, Kevin Nash, Adam Rodriguez, Andie MacDowell, Michael Strahan
Production & Credits: Iron Horse Entertainment
Distributors: Warner Bros., Roadshow Films
